- `/Users/damianpiatkowski/Documents/workspace/inception-engine/src/index.ts` - The only file being modified; contains all five change sites
- `/Users/damianpiatkowski/Documents/workspace/inception-engine/src/errors.ts` - `UserError` definition; confirms the constructor signature (`message: string`) matches all throw sites
- `/Users/damianpiatkowski/Documents/workspace/inception-engine/src/types.ts` - Confirms `CliOptions.command` already includes `"help"`, so no type changes are needed there

